PRIVATE EVENTS
Private Outdoor Tent
Rent our tent for your wedding rehearsal, birthday party, corporate meetings, and any other private event at our events tent! A 1500 square-foot open air tent with electricity. We also provide tons of amenities such as a speaker system, bar setup, catering, tables, chairs, and more! For more information, email us at
sami@homesteadtinyenterprises.com
GALLERY
BOOKING
BOOKING
Catering
Reach out to our private events manager for current information regarding catering!
​
Private Events Manager:
sami@homesteadtinyenterprises.com
MORE INFO
Tent Rental Rates & Bar Pricing
Monday-Wednesday:
Full Park Rental; $2000/4 hours ($900 bar minimum required)
Thursday:
$500/4 hours ($300 bar minimum required)
Friday & Saturday:
$900/4 hours ($600 bar minimum required)
Sunday:
$800/4 hours ($500 bar minimum required)
Speaker System with Bluetooth:
$150
Axe Throwing Group Rate (16 people):
$250/hour
(to accommodate larger parties, more hours must be reserved)
​
Bar Setup in tent:
$200 for bar setup
Requires at least 1 Bartender – $50/hour per bartender
